show.title: The Couple Came From Hell
show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/3HFASW
show.description: Chinn's husband, Lumor, jumped from the rooftop to prove his innocence, while Chinn was tragically killed in the chaos. However, she was reborn with memories of her past and resolved to change her fate. In her new life, Chinn uncovered the conspiracies behind Stacy and Camor. Determined to secure her husband's and her own future, she began to turn the tables and set up her own counterattacks, ultimately achieving victory.
